  <brief_title>Chemotherapy and Proton Radiation for the Treatment of Locally Advanced Lung Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase I/II Study of Combined Chemotherapy and High Dose, Accelerated Proton Radiation for the Treatment of Locally Advanced Non-Small Cell Lung Carcinoma</official_title>
